Content (CC BY-NC 4.0)
----------------------

Applies to: the educational text, the bilingual organ / acupoint /
herb / formula data in `assets/data.js` and `assets/glossary.js`, the
classical-Chinese authored prose throughout the HTML pages, and the
illustrations and reference images in `assets/img/` and
`assets/tongue/`.

You may share and adapt this content for **non-commercial** purposes,
provided you give appropriate credit (link back to
https://drmusic.netlify.app/ and to https://github.com/KunVinn/CTM-Clock)
and indicate if changes were made.

Full license text:
https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/legalcode

