https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/

Note on third-party material: certain reference photographs in
`assets/tongue/` (the CCTV-4 tongue body color/shape charts and the
齿痕舌 pattern posters) are derivative educational excerpts whose
underlying copyright belongs to their respective broadcasters and
authors. They are included here under fair-use educational provisions
and are NOT covered by the CC BY-NC license above. If you fork this
repository, please remove or replace those files unless your use also
qualifies as fair-use.


Medical disclaimer
------------------

Nothing in this repository is medical advice. The site is an
